### Classes Module API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mathematics 101",
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "schedule": "Monday, Wednesday, Friday 9:00 AM - 10:00 AM",
  "teacherId": "TEACHER_ID_HERE"
}

### 2. Create Another Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Physics 201",
  "subject": "Physics",
  "schedule": "Tuesday, Thursday 2:00 PM - 3:00 PM",
  "teacherId": "TEACHER_ID_HERE"
}

### 3. Create Third Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "English Literature",
  "subject": "English",
  "schedule": "Monday, Wednesday 11:00 AM - 12:00 PM"
}

### 4. Get All Classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Classes with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes?page=1&limit=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Search Classes by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes?search=Mathematics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Search Classes by Subject
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes?subject=Mathematics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Class Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Classes by Subject
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/subject/Mathematics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get Classes by Teacher
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/teacher/TEACHER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Class by ID (replace with actual ID from create response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Class by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/name/Mathematics 101
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Get Students in Class
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Update Class (replace with actual ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/classes/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Advanced Mathematics 101",
  "schedule": "Monday, Wednesday, Friday 9:00 AM - 10:30 AM"
}

### 15. Assign Teacher to Class
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/classes/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID/assign-teacher
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teacherId": "TEACHER_ID_HERE"
}

### 16. Remove Teacher from Class
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/classes/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID/remove-teacher
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. Test Duplicate Class Error
POST {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mathematics 101",
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "schedule": "Different schedule"
}

### 18. Test Non-existent Class
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. Test Unauthorized Access (without token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes

### 20. Delete Class (replace with actual ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/classes/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 21. Verify Class Deletion - Get Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
